snippet.title: F1® Manager 2022 | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Order the digital version of F1 Manager 2022 to play now! https://www.f1manager.com/buy 

All the research and development is done. Practice and qualifying is complete. Your strategy is set. The five red lights are about to go out…

We are incredibly excited to launch F1® Manager 2022 on Steam, Epic Games Store, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and PlayStation 4!

Early access begins now for those who have pre-ordered digitally across any platform, but you can still join the early access by purchasing the digital version before the full launch on August 30. F1® Manager 2022 will also launch physically in stores on Xbox and PlayStation on August 30.

Find out more:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/F1Manager
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/f1manager/?hl=en
Facebook -https://www.facebook.com/F1ManagerGame/
Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/f1manager
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@f1manager

#F1 #f1manager
